# SimpleEngine default keymap
# Main editor keymap

This allows different keymaps for inputs vs textareas if desired.

!! Settings

Configure in ''Control Panel → Settings → CodeMirror → Editor Settings'' under the SimpleEngine section.

!! Technical Notes

* Uses the same plugin system as the main editor
* Shares configuration with main editor where appropriate
* Input mode filters out newlines (single-line only)
* Supports `editFocusPopup` for dropdown integration
